<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Tractable" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Tractable,</orth> manageable, governable, compliant: <cit><quote>thou shalt find me t. to any honest reason,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.194" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 194</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if thou dost find him t. to us,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 3.1.174" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 1, 174</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this t. obedience,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.64" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 2, 64</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.160" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 160</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.470" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 470</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 4.6.211" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 6, 211</bibl>.
